item.description:
It's time to become aware of the importance of what is going on energetically in our environment.

Bring your notebooks if you want to learn about some energy emanations which are generally unknown, as well as how to shield yourself against them.

Some do severe damage, even causing mutations of our DNA.

Since the intensity of these energies is steadily increasing, it is important to learn how to protect yourself as soon as possible.

Waiting till year 2012 is not a good idea, especially if you wish to avoid irreversible damage.
